{"_id":"GdJgNhxyeYLjBxEC","name":"Tier 3 Melee Critical Hits (Levels 9-12)","description":"Critical hit effects for melee attacks at Tier 3 (Levels 9-12). Effects are powerful for experienced adventurers.","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-slashing-red.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"7qKYvNOZQPfbNfqj","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical strike deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":12,"range":[1,12],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"A2JdsTPmZenClko7","type":0,"text":"Ringing Skull - Your crushing blow leaves the target's ears ringing. They are deafened until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":8,"range":[13,20],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"pqwzLYljJW7P3scu","type":0,"text":"Crippled Arm - Your strike wrecks the muscles of the target's weapon arm. They take -2 to attack rolls until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[21,27],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"dgAvTgODr5I2q11t","type":0,"text":"Pain Overload - Waves of pain wrack the target's body. They have disadvantage on all attacks until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[28,34],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Pain Overload","duration":1}}},{"_id":"yqfPT8zGRPxr6zJC","type":0,"text":"Disorienting Blow - Your devastating hit leaves the target reeling. They have disadvantage on all saving throws until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":7,"range":[35,41],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Disoriented","duration":1}}},{"_id":"8Jktpa2RuLCMA8mj","type":0,"text":"Armor Shattered - Your attack caves in a section of the target's armor. They take -3 AC until it is repaired by a skilled smith.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[42,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-3,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"z78NwLFLON3uOmZk","type":0,"text":"Driving Slam - You drive your full weight into the blow. The target must succeed on a DC 15 Strength save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"2FcJOzk33PW87AxS","type":0,"text":"Deep Wound - Your strike opens a terrible wound. The target takes two extra weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"EQOFnYaSUn5ksYE1","type":0,"text":"Blood in the Eyes - A spray of blood fills the target's eyes. They are blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"38iMMBeC8gvBLdrp","type":0,"text":"Gut Wound - Your blade rips through the target's gut. They must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution save or be poisoned until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"hnIGGh9EQZt2utoI","type":0,"text":"Pinning Strike - Your weapon hooks the target and holds them fast. They are grappled until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"grappled","duration":1}}},{"_id":"kC9VxEjrpv2GG7cg","type":0,"text":"Hamstrung - Your blade severs a tendon in the target's leg. They are restrained until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"restrained","duration":1}}},{"_id":"qvJkG60AmqKF3BhD","type":0,"text":"Exposed Defenses - Your attack lays the target's guard wide open. Attacks against them have advantage for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Exposed Defenses","duration":3}}},{"_id":"swhSQGrawA0dNJQ3","type":0,"text":"Terrorizing Blow - Your savage strike breaks the target's courage. They must succeed on a DC 15 Wisdom save or be frightened of you for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":3}}},{"_id":"heYEwgrC0ISGh0nN","type":0,"text":"Disemboweling Strike - Your blade tears through vital organs. The target must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution save or be incapacitated until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"incapacitated","duration":1}}},{"_id":"migpBZjGQjzfcQ5g","type":0,"text":"Brutal Devastation - Your mighty strike hammers home. The target takes three extra weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"bvoKenEQGyT8ElQT","type":0,"text":"Weapon Lodged - Your weapon buries itself and tears free, dealing an extra weapon die of damage.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"B5xoXbEBfLRvoT6h","type":0,"text":"Ribcracker - Your blow shatters the target's ribs and drives the breath from them. They must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution save or be stunned until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"stunned","duration":1}}},{"_id":"tdhgoLFwjcHmNhNn","type":0,"text":"Near-Fatal Blow - Your strike finds something vital. The target must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution save or take an extra 4d10 damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"4d10","damageType":"weapon"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":3,"attackType":"melee","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849386,"modifiedTime":1783951849386,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"72ZxQshxo3Ibh334","name":"Tier 3 Melee Fumbles (Levels 9-12)","description":"Fumble effects for melee attacks at Tier 3 (Levels 9-12). Effects are more severe for experienced adventurers.","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-slashing-red.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"L8zjYBj1hHsEyYfZ","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - You stumble but recover with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":12,"range":[1,12],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"rw1C4yOCJXvv9K3K","type":0,"text":"Off Your Feet - You lurch off balance and have disadvantage on your next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":8,"range":[13,20],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Off Your Feet","duration":0}}},{"_id":"arwPdEJOWIP2MsQn","type":0,"text":"Jarred Wrist - You jar your wrist on the botched swing, taking a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[21,27],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"XU4RpPiaPCGfAu6S","type":0,"text":"Lost Grip - Your weapon twists in your hand. You have disadvantage on your next melee weapon attack.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":7,"range":[28,34],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.mwak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Lost Grip","duration":0}}},{"_id":"tZgBqWwoZY9NeMWD","type":0,"text":"Dropped Guard - You drop your guard, taking a -2 penalty to your AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[35,41],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"0kCyRduCwEeprkKq","type":0,"text":"Weapon Badly Damaged - Your weapon is badly damaged. You take a -3 penalty to attack rolls until it is repaired.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[42,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-3,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"BOzVlnHwDf87hZm3","type":0,"text":"Massive Opening - Your catastrophic failure leaves you exposed. Attacks against you have advantage for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Massive Opening","duration":3}}},{"_id":"gFCNroiYlAh8dXbA","type":0,"text":"Severe Muscle Tear - You badly injure yourself. Take 2d6 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"uYqh2jdH16s2Lujf","type":0,"text":"Sprawled - Your wild swing throws you off balance and you fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"1NuQhWWfb4Zi8Y7d","type":0,"text":"Shaken Confidence - Your failure rattles you. You have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Shaken Confidence","duration":1}}},{"_id":"sOi29o2Px9jtWitb","type":0,"text":"Ears Ringing - Your own clumsy blow rings your helm like a bell. You are deafened until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":1}}},{"_id":"XHNruuH677V0PXRd","type":0,"text":"Weapon Flung - Your weapon flies from your grasp, landing well out of reach.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disarm"}}},{"_id":"V4AWPl02A7Irm79Y","type":0,"text":"Rattled - Your fumble rattles your nerve. You are frightened until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":1}}},{"_id":"6lydfrvH9rav5Lv6","type":0,"text":"Hit Yourself Hard - Your weapon rebounds and strikes you. Take 2d8 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d8","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"S9bIhKsm85IrMNHA","type":0,"text":"Concussed - You crack your own skull with the pommel. You are stunned until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"stunned","duration":1}}},{"_id":"HnLq5Ues9GKuLZDy","type":0,"text":"Blown Wind - The reckless effort leaves you gasping. You gain one level of exhaustion.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"o2iJTd6tJTpgDUFY","type":0,"text":"Severe Self-Wound - Your weapon rebounds critically. Take 3d8 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3d8","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"crgsKfIk4lJjqnF5","type":0,"text":"Wild Swing - Your uncontrolled swing hits your nearest ally. Roll an attack against that ally's AC; on a hit, deal weapon damage.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}},{"_id":"Vt5P8CbqPIn7JiLu","type":0,"text":"Devastating Rebound - Your weapon whips back at you. Make a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or take 3d6 damage and fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"prone","damageFormula":"3d6","damageType":"weapon"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":3,"attackType":"melee","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849386,"modifiedTime":1783951849386,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"w04jZbV1A89bcmtf","name":"Tier 3 Ranged Critical Hits (Levels 9-12)","description":"Critical hit effects for ranged attacks at Tier 3 (Levels 9-12). Effects are powerful for experienced adventurers.","img":"icons/weapons/bows/longbow-recurve-brown.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"wBZfpPkcipr1DgtI","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical strike deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":12,"range":[1,12],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"ANZAGk1ilhnLvt3a","type":0,"text":"Severed Tendon - Your shot severs a tendon in the target's arm, giving them -2 to attack rolls until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[13,20],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"LZb7EF6mlSu0CStF","type":0,"text":"Muffled Ears - The shot clips the side of the target's head, leaving them deafened until the wound is treated.","img":"icons/svg/silenced.svg","weight":7,"range":[21,27],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"SfEHg4JaH2l3x38z","type":0,"text":"Armor Piercing - Your shot punches through a plate, imposing -3 AC until the armor is repaired.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[28,34],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-3,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"GT8uMoatWDCnKkMe","type":0,"text":"Suppressing Shot - A hail of covering fire pins the target's nerve, giving them disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":7,"range":[35,41],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Suppressed","duration":1}}},{"_id":"1SjkpgE7iko8YQkT","type":0,"text":"Staggering Shot - Your shot staggers the target badly, giving them disadvantage on attacks and saving throws until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":6,"range":[42,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.all","save.all"],"effectName":"Staggered","duration":1}}},{"_id":"Z4RGtmeGAl3STreT","type":0,"text":"Exposed Target - Your shot lays bare the target's defenses, granting advantage on attacks against them for three rounds.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Exposed Target","duration":3}}},{"_id":"74tjXGg3LR5fqa5C","type":0,"text":"Grit in the Eye - A spray of grit and blood catches the target across the eyes, leaving them blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"ie7EXkznzRumIVas","type":0,"text":"Bleeder - The wound opens wide and bleeds freely, dealing an extra 2d6 piercing damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"piercing"}}},{"_id":"iSMHGnXbeS2qlbhU","type":0,"text":"Penetrating Shot - Your projectile drives through with devastating force, dealing an extra two weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/thrust.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"ObCPO1uA5I2oDoWY","type":0,"text":"Kneecapped - Your shot shatters the target's knee, forcing a DC 15 Dexterity save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"dex","effectCondition":"prone"}}},{"_id":"qnh5bIkSCo5nQ2CW","type":0,"text":"Blinding Shot - Your shot rakes across the target's eyes, blinding them for three rounds.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":3}}},{"_id":"UbWChai6xYWJmD44","type":0,"text":"Nailed Down - The projectile nails the target to the ground, leaving them restrained until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"restrained","duration":1}}},{"_id":"w6BbPD0DLefNPc4S","type":0,"text":"Deep Puncture - Your projectile buries itself deep, dealing an extra maximized weapon die of damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1WB","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"hBThNWM20eLKHaHv","type":0,"text":"Sinking Terror - A shot to a vital spot fills the target with dread, forcing a DC 15 Wisdom save or be frightened of you.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened"}}},{"_id":"OpCiAWb9ESy2X7gc","type":0,"text":"Punctured Lung - Your shot punctures a lung, forcing a DC 15 Constitution save or be poisoned while the target struggles to breathe.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned"}}},{"_id":"nBmJESnZazUXk0pN","type":0,"text":"Devastating Shot - Your perfectly placed shot deals an extra three weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"A7R56k4XVVI6nYav","type":0,"text":"Skull Ringer - The impact rattles the target's skull, forcing a DC 15 Constitution save or be stunned until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"stunned"}}},{"_id":"oLWfEECUyQvvfrNm","type":0,"text":"Heart Shot - Your shot drives toward a vital organ, forcing a DC 15 Constitution save or take an extra 4d10 damage.","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"4d10","damageType":"piercing"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":3,"attackType":"ranged","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849387,"modifiedTime":1783951849387,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"f4E5ohFOSpbqJiOK","name":"Tier 3 Ranged Fumbles (Levels 9-12)","description":"Fumble effects for ranged attacks at Tier 3 (Levels 9-12). Effects are more severe for experienced adventurers.","img":"icons/weapons/bows/longbow-recurve-brown.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"dXw0NcGfKanQpOMR","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your shot goes wide but you recover with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":12,"range":[1,12],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"6YcipF2BxRa8nuB4","type":0,"text":"Watering Eyes - Your eyes water from the effort and you have disadvantage on your next ability check.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[13,20],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"ability.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Watering Eyes","duration":0}}},{"_id":"P3r93aZRx4JFXNNB","type":0,"text":"Flinch - You flinch at your own misfire and have disadvantage on your next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[21,27],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Flinch","duration":0}}},{"_id":"ITQ4KjDSr8BOgftO","type":0,"text":"Snapped String - Your bowstring snaps taut awkwardly and you have disadvantage on ranged attacks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[28,34],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.rwak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Snapped String","duration":1}}},{"_id":"VtW8A7DkVhsYJe8c","type":0,"text":"Fouled Aim - Your aim is thrown off and you have disadvantage on your next attack roll.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[35,41],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Fouled Aim","duration":0}}},{"_id":"c7EHdjf5maVCv55T","type":0,"text":"Overdrawn - You overdraw and wrench your form, taking a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[42,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"8HIsooGZs4MqPI43","type":0,"text":"Recoil Strain - The recoil wrenches your arm; take 1d8 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d8","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"GEHh2emcUXrVGrPB","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Shot - You telegraph your shot and your target has advantage on its next saving throw against you.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed Shot","duration":0}}},{"_id":"1tR19lx9EdUhfQ6f","type":0,"text":"Caught Flat - You are caught flat-footed; attacks against you have advantage until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Caught Flat","duration":1}}},{"_id":"WrIWOSllvqTGLiNi","type":0,"text":"Jammed Solid - Your weapon jams solid and you have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Jammed Solid","duration":1}}},{"_id":"EKIh2pG3LiCY7RIK","type":0,"text":"Exposed Flank - Your stance collapses, leaving a -3 penalty to your AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-3,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"eSeUgW582jSjKn7A","type":0,"text":"Dropped Weapon - Your ranged weapon flies from your hands, landing 25 feet away.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disarm"}}},{"_id":"iuT9D6vUNSZdQrsr","type":0,"text":"Off-Balance - You lose your footing; make a DC 15 Dexterity saving throw or fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"dex","effectCondition":"prone","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"gU4oJNCijrj5DWIr","type":0,"text":"Winded - The strain wracks your body; make a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or take 2d6 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"TzJCRlUBwlJCjsFG","type":0,"text":"Stinging Rebound - Your shot rebounds savagely into you; take 2d8 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d8","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"agV0JHrCKWc71f0f","type":0,"text":"Blinded - A backlash of string and splinters blinds you until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":1}}},{"_id":"pD08Mqjr0yKOdSNl","type":0,"text":"Incapacitated - Your fumble leaves you reeling; you are incapacitated until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"incapacitated","duration":1}}},{"_id":"fMQDcecQ9GUmVgJW","type":0,"text":"Tangled Sling - Your sling or strap wraps around you; you are restrained until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"restrained","duration":1}}},{"_id":"7FOUY7h7PUsUPpsJ","type":0,"text":"Wild Ricochet - Your shot ricochets wildly toward the nearest ally; roll an attack against their AC.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":3,"attackType":"ranged","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849387,"modifiedTime":1783951849387,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"vQHTF6ajHsivYqjC","name":"Tier 3 Spell Critical Hits (Levels 9-12)","description":"Critical hit effects for spell attacks at Tier 3 (Levels 9-12). Effects are powerful for experienced adventurers.","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"hfuUUxSGOvQm9zOv","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical spell deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":12,"range":[1,12],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"qkzDSLuNBTt9LHXA","type":0,"text":"Sluggish Mind - The target's thoughts turn to sludge, giving them disadvantage on saving throws until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":8,"range":[13,20],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Sluggish Mind","duration":1}}},{"_id":"VU7GdJsgf7Z48sxn","type":0,"text":"Hex of Frailty - A hex of frailty erodes the target's defenses, giving them a -2 penalty to AC until removed.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[21,27],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"8JQ7XqRMDPWDYjnG","type":0,"text":"Magic Disruption - Your spell disrupts their magical abilities. Target has disadvantage on spell attacks and saving throws for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/silenced.svg","weight":7,"range":[28,34],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.msak","attack.rsak","save.all"],"effectName":"Magic Disruption","duration":3}}},{"_id":"1X2BHOEQGsz00H05","type":0,"text":"Searing Flash - A blinding burst of arcane light sears the target's eyes, leaving them blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":7,"range":[35,41],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"Qu15rdk9oz9YGHCR","type":0,"text":"Mana Burn - Raw magic ignites the target's own reserves, dealing 2d6 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":6,"range":[42,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"BCiSkomcfrT18yyr","type":0,"text":"Withering Curse - A withering hex corrodes the target from within; they must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution save or be poisoned.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned"}}},{"_id":"7PU2kjC3ygsFMfJt","type":0,"text":"Arcane Immolation - Magical energy sears the target. They take extra force damage equal to two of the spell's damage dice at the start of their next turn.","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-yellow-orange.webp","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"5OlpgFqg99Xdi01U","type":0,"text":"Concussive Blast - A concussive shockwave hammers the target; they must succeed on a DC 15 Strength save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"prone"}}},{"_id":"OF3ZTihPXv5VZfRQ","type":0,"text":"Elemental Devastation - Your spell's element overwhelms the target. Add extra damage equal to three of the spell's damage dice, of the spell's type.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3S","damageType":"spell"}}},{"_id":"b6jSUqDlisLTnwBi","type":0,"text":"Numbing Frost - Creeping frost locks the target's limbs; they must succeed on a DC 15 Strength save or be restrained.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"restrained"}}},{"_id":"4828HdWYDsETuAXO","type":0,"text":"Mind Spike - A lance of psychic force stabs the target's mind; they must succeed on a DC 15 Wisdom save or be frightened of you.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened"}}},{"_id":"7TfPWAZnTgLWfvrr","type":0,"text":"Arcane Amplification - Your magical power surges! Deal additional force damage equal to three of the spell's damage dice.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"boJuFk7AzMXjKI7g","type":0,"text":"Terrifying Magic - Your spell terrifies the target. They are frightened of you for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":3}}},{"_id":"kcFVwXR9tlS2Gtel","type":0,"text":"Arcane Vulnerability - Your magic leaves the target exposed. Attacks against them have advantage for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Arcane Vulnerability","duration":3}}},{"_id":"BUbseT4CUIhGfK4a","type":0,"text":"Soulscored - The spell scars the target's very soul, inflicting one level of exhaustion.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"1dSbGID8WnZmcPCm","type":0,"text":"Powerful Blast - The force sends the target flying 30 feet, prone, and stunned until end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/thrust.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"stunned","duration":1}}},{"_id":"N0ivWFquB8dvhDdt","type":0,"text":"Arcane Lock - Binding sigils seize the target's body; they must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution save or be paralyzed.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"paralyzed"}}},{"_id":"bVVpCy7tLYgr524V","type":0,"text":"Elemental Detonation - The spell's energy detonates catastrophically, dealing bonus damage equal to the spell's slot-scaled magnitude.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1SB","damageType":"spell"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":3,"attackType":"spell","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849387,"modifiedTime":1783951849387,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"S477fQAg3hMGHcHg","name":"Tier 3 Spell Fumbles (Levels 9-12)","description":"Fumble effects for spell attacks at Tier 3 (Levels 9-12). Effects are powerful for veteran adventurers.","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"FaTdPhR9SPLITu5j","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your spell fizzles harmlessly with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":12,"range":[1,12],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"SNcU5PQgMHch8ODo","type":0,"text":"Grounded Magic - Your spell earths itself through your body. You have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[13,20],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Grounded Magic","duration":1}}},{"_id":"3LofJekyqRS5KLzV","type":0,"text":"Spell Recoil - The spell lashes back as it leaves you. You have disadvantage on your next ranged spell attack.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":7,"range":[21,27],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.rsak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Spell Recoil","duration":0}}},{"_id":"NQfWOFMItgkazEsh","type":0,"text":"Arcane Hiccup - Your magic stutters and misfires. You have disadvantage on spell attacks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[28,34],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.msak","attack.rsak"],"advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Arcane Hiccup","duration":1}}},{"_id":"SLzM9cTWWD58Jd5b","type":0,"text":"Somatic Cramp - Your casting hand cramps violently. You have disadvantage on concentration checks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":7,"range":[35,41],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"concentration","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Somatic Cramp","duration":1}}},{"_id":"LDk7pMbhlUB64nvK","type":0,"text":"Arcane Backlash - Raw magic rebounds into you. Take force damage equal to one of the spell's damage dice.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":6,"range":[42,47],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"2hPyvl5htjRaV3Xt","type":0,"text":"Component Combustion - Your material components ignite in your grip. Take 1d6 fire damage.","img":"icons/svg/fire.svg","weight":6,"range":[48,53],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"fire"}}},{"_id":"HV61pTYarPClHsoQ","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Magic - Your fumbled casting tips your hand. Enemies have advantage on their next saving throw against your spells.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":6,"range":[54,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed Magic","duration":0}}},{"_id":"uYYWP0K4MDC7V6Rb","type":0,"text":"Exposed Weave - Your botched weave leaves you unguarded. Attacks against you have advantage until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Exposed Weave","duration":1}}},{"_id":"qRck2S3xksbMtD9a","type":0,"text":"Warped Focus - The recoil throws off your aim. You take a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"Ode0hKWYhs9ZuLaz","type":0,"text":"Shattered Wards - The backlash shreds your protective wards. You take a -2 penalty to AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"S1jVtFt1ZxvsWPkR","type":0,"text":"Backlash Sprawl - The detonation throws you off your feet. You are knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"DdqGNWYh00nVJ5Su","type":0,"text":"Deafening Boom - The spell erupts with a deafening crack. You are deafened.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"e3G9wvp9lPlisXwI","type":0,"text":"Blinding Feedback - A blinding flash of misfired magic sears your eyes. You are blinded until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"4tqnzDhZOYltnfVY","type":0,"text":"Searing Recoil - Searing magical energy tears back into you. Take 1d10 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d10","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"cYxmccmXW4gPUEkT","type":0,"text":"Catastrophic Rebound - Your spell collapses inward. Make a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or take 4d6 force damage and be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":15,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"4d6","damageType":"force","effectCondition":"prone","failEffect":"Take force damage and be knocked prone"}}},{"_id":"bjC7u2GwFbXSLBFF","type":0,"text":"Mana Drain - The failed casting rips the vigor from you. You gain one level of exhaustion.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"W2rwgL1BPWkUSVYD","type":0,"text":"Wild Surge Jolt - Wild magic detonates through your body. Take 2d6 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"T06QmFvBbBtffB0o","type":0,"text":"Misfired Blast - Your spell veers wildly and misfires at the nearest ally. Make a spell attack against the nearest ally; on a hit, they take the spell's damage.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":3,"attackType":"spell","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849387,"modifiedTime":1783951849387,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}